4. RESTRICTIONS (COMMERCIAL & AI)

Commercial Use of the Software is strictly prohibited without a separate,
written commercial license signed by the Licensor.

4.1 Prohibited Commercial Uses

- Direct Sale: Selling, renting, leasing, or sublicensing the Software or any
